title: Motley Crue - Quaternary (limited edition 1994 album)
description:
This is teh limited edition american release of the 1994 album Quaternary with John Corabi on vocals. There were a limited number of this album released to fans by mail only. This is an extremly rare album for any Crue head.

track list is:

2. Father

3. Bittersuite
